room_title: Escape room "Cellblock at Shawshank" by TeamEscape 262 in Milwaukee
room_address: N80W14942 Appleton Avenue, Menomonee Falls, WI 53051
room_description: Some of your associates have been accused of a very serious crime. They are behind bars in the notorious Shawshank prison. Your first job is to find them. Then you can infiltrate the warden's office to free your friends before this crooked warden returns from the bank. Along with escaping, your team also has the very difficult task of indicting the warden as you put together a financial puzzle to seal his fate! Fail and you will go directly to solitary!
